Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  如此美麗的我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的小豬從天上掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥？所以我討厭下等生物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看是小貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一樣掉下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方爬不上去  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這種事  你竟敢叫我豬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這身體只是借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來的我可是擁有高貴的身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你笑  所以說人類真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對  我怎麼能陪她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快爬出這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小貓咪  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我一個人留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說人類真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪你有酒臭味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一樣不景氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,股運真差…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子阿姨說冰箱裏的蝦不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那真是奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吃了吧  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了不要給家裏人添麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙  你是在懷疑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為幾隻蝦就囉嗦個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我跟西村借來的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎麼賠我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然是你不該放在這種地方  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你沒愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目你這不良  禿頭  白蘆筍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志  什麼事這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目你這不良  禿頭  白蘆筍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  夏目大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那只白色的肥貓也真讓人頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都到八原來喝掉很多酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝掉喝掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是酒  吃東西胃口也不小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會唱歌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音癡音癡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒品還很差
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  喝了一定會暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人是八原的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那隻大胃耍酒瘋音癡的肥貓是他的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  我們的忍耐也有限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有限度有限度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  為了八原的和平  抵制那隻大胃耍酒瘋音癡老年臭的肥貓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭了臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為了八原的和平  抵制那隻大胃耍酒瘋音癡老年臭的肥貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑…斑大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胃  耍酒瘋  音癡  老年臭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了冰箱裏13只蝦  踩壞了CD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝦（AB）？CD？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EFG？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把八原驅逐乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是忘恩負義的傢伙們的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨化到讓他們無法居住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有種奇怪的惡寒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了  還有作業呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很貴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是買了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過的制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你是哪個學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  什麼嘛  原來是你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏目的同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  你是夏目的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是那傢伙的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛才斷交了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們  陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在遊戲中心花了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混合披薩再來一份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶汁烤菜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  吃得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  我的胃很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  病弱的是我們的錢包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來遊戲中心是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僊貝的一種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱狗  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有披薩和奶汁烤菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  讓我好生破費
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  老師  我們差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:20.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧上吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  超過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被怪人抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒看到貓咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志你知道它在哪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有餓肚子啊  喵吉君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵吉？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直穩穩地坐在我的坐墊上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它不在覺得很寂寞呢  還有喵五郎也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵五郎是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師  意料之外地跟藤原家混熟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省吧  不成熟的傢伙  我才不會這麼快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪…笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.05,0:11:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西村  這是你借我的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子啊  女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  可以一轉眼就把咖啡店菜單從頭到尾全吃光的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被拖到遊戲中心去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不讓我們回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托她的福這個月的零花錢全沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識這樣的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.18,0:12:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認錯人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我根本沒有女性朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？不對  她說是你的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我詳細情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放學路上去遊戲中心是違反校規的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目君也會玩遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正  比早上去翻垃圾倒是好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  民子？你好  一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  跟媽媽一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天要去野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子的爸爸和媽媽都請到假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子家父母都工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去捉弄夏目的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了  是我  是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是猿猴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  聽說你跟擁有友人帳的人類斷交了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然斷交了  友人帳我就能拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧  我說過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後別來怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼  斑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有留戀了  斑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨不得友人帳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是對人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.46,0:16:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目這笨蛋變成怎樣我不管\N只是不能忍受友人帳被其他人奪走而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說我傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的身體真能吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦  好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全粘上貴志了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在朋友出差的兩三天托我們照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  什麼夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼友人帳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我傻了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你們看什麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抽你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星～真美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天婦羅蓋澆布魯士舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這水…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  嘰嘰喳喳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘰喳  嗚咕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  有巧克力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  貓咪給你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.12,0:18:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來要跟爸爸媽媽分三份吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但野餐又被取消了  我就一個人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了貓咪  要不要來我家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:19:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起用餐和吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一塊吃一定很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲了  快出來吧  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  原來是你幹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說兔子淋雨會死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪也會死掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎  會嗎  怎麼辦…貓咪要死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小貓咪對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我阻止你回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小貓咪  你都留下來陪我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小貓咪要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是脆弱的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就弱還要關心別人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒什麼力量  還要拚命的保護別人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飛？真是美夢  溫暖又柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師   你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰了我的印記  老師就變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為被你中的詛咒所影響
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:43.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是丙？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五日印的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你的命還剩下五天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}（日语中「五日」和「何時か」同音）
